{"tid":814037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[窮撚集資] 梁振英：或眾籌告林卓廷等人","createTime":"2018-09-11T02:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T02:37:55.000Z","uid":77196,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d38af69a32bb0e1cd08607060ed4b9efe36141b3","tid":814037,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"英國國家打擊罪案調查局(NCA)指，由於前特首梁振英涉干犯的罪行，並非在英國發生，故不調查UGL事件，梁振英今早在社交網站指，會委託英國律師「循malice（惡意）及其他方向研究在英國起訴林卓廷等人。」梁振英還指，或以眾籌起訴林：「這些人用衆籌的錢(OPM, other people&rsquo;s money)纒擾中傷我，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日後我不排除用OPM向林卓廷等和他們背後的人討個公道，這是對等和平等</strong></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英說，雖然自己手上有很多其他事等著做，「但香港社會不能這樣爛在這些所謂民主派的人手裏。」<br />\n<br />\n對於英國NCA不作調查，梁指，英國人沒有偏袒他的理由，「如果這份協議有問題，四年來我和UGL或其他人可能不被刑事或民事檢控嗎？這是常識。」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，NCA 指他「No offences committed in the UK (沒有在英國違法)」，是將所有指控一掃而空，「重重的打了林卓廷等人的耳光」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，NCA的回覆全文，其實只是指梁振英涉干犯罪行不在英國發生，而是在香港，故該局才不調查。「The NCA did not open an investigation into the allegations made against the former Hong Kong leader Leung Chun-Ying. The alleged offences took place in Hong Kong with no offences committed in the UK and as such are not a matter for the NCA.」"},{"pid":"85a0372b4336b5bdb9b8282a23668fc218335fa6","tid":814037,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b44d04c4f47cddd6e1ff2bf529f75c6ec6a0196","tid":814037,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"堂堂國家副主席唔係窮撚到咁呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35dec07ae5b0248f216e6bf2476b4b45cfb9535","tid":814037,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b44d04c4f47cddd6e1ff2bf529f75c6ec6a0196","tid":814037,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"堂堂國家副主席唔係窮撚到咁呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj